Anna: Last weekend I visited my grandma.
Tom: That is nice! What did you do?
Anna: We baked cookies together.
Tom: Yum! Were they good?
Anna: Yes, they were delicious.
Tom: What else did you do?
Anna: We watched old photos and she told me stories.
Tom: Will you visit her again?
Anna: Yes, I will visit her next month.
Tom: Say hello to her for me!
